1999-08-23  Laurent Pautet  <pautet@dorine.enst.fr>

	* broca-buffers.ad[bs]: New unit to handle buffers.
	
	* all files: Update files to take new unit into account.

1999-08-21  Laurent Pautet  <pautet@dorine.enst.fr>

	* broca-giop.ads: Change header size to 12. Define No_Context to
	exotic value in order to check context alignment.

	* broca-giop.adb, broca-server.adb: Receive body message at index
 	Message_Header_Size in a buffer to preserve interoperability.
	Do not always align body size to 16.

	* broca-marshalling.adb, broca-marshalling.ads: Define Dump
 	procedure to dump buffers.

	* broca-stream.adb: Dump incoming and outgoing stream.
	